headline: CSX Celebrates Reopening of Blue Ridge Subdivision
summary: One year after Hurricane Helene, freight trains return to the Nolichucky GorgeJACKSONVILLE, Fla., Oct. 02, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- CSX (NASDAQ: CSX) today celebrated the reopening of the Blue Ridge Subdivision, nearly a year to the day after Hurricane Helene destroyed large portions of the freight line.
